  <tr>
    <td><strong>Description:</strong></td>
    <td>Use the <code>chrome.app.runtime</code> module
    to manage the app lifecycle.
    The app runtime manages app installation,
    controls the event page, and
    can shut down the app at anytime.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Availability:</strong></td>
    <td>Google Chrome 23</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Permissions:</strong></td>
    <td>None</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Learn more:</strong></td>
